Agency Sensor Doctrine v1.0

Core Insight

Agency is a sense organ.

Humans do not merely perceive reality through observation. They perceive reality through participation.

Some information is only revealed after interaction.

⸻

First Principle

Action is not output. Action is measurement.

Traditional model:

Observation → Knowledge → Action

Agency Sensor model:

Observation → Action → Knowledge

Certain truths are inaccessible until reality is probed.

